DELETE :- (a, pos, n, val)

- a is an array.
- pos indicates position at which you want to delete element.
- n imdicates number of elements in an array.
- val indicates value (elements) to be deleted.
   1. [initialize counter] i=n
   2. [Move the elements one position up] 
        Repeat While (i<=n-1)
            1. a[i] = a[i + 1]
            2. i = i + 1
   3. [Reset size of array]
          n = n -1
   4. [Finished] & Exit
